A lightweight socket-based library to create HTTP(s) and WebSocket connections.
## Features
   * Cookies support
   * Caching support
   * Easy debugging
   * HTTP authentication
   * Form support
   * No requirements(save Python)
   * Keep-Alive and connection pooling
